Usage: avgavg [-options] -i <instem1> -i <instem2> -o <outstem>
    <instem1>           : prefix of first .bfloat input file
    <instem2>           : prefix of second .bfloat input file
    <outstem>           : prefix of .bfloat output file
  options:
    -firstslice <int>   : first slice number to process
    -nslices <int>      : number of slices to process
    -nbins <int>        : total number of bins or conditions
